
🤖 Gemini AI Chatbot

A simple AI Chatbot web app built with HTML, CSS, JavaScript that integrates Google Gemini API. Supports both text and image inputs for interactive conversations.

🚀 Features

💬 Chat with Gemini AI using text messages.

🖼️ Upload images and ask the AI to analyze them.

📱 Responsive design with modern UI.

⚡ Real-time chat experience with typing/loading animation.

🛠️ Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript

AI: Google Gemini API (gemini-1.5-flash)

📌 How It Works

Enter your message or upload an image.

The chatbot sends the content to Gemini API.

AI response is displayed in the chat interface.
